OL,3,C'Vile' predator jailed for attempting
OL,4,Cto rape 13-year-old girl on train
OL,6,FA 50-year-old from Tajikistan has been
OL,7,Fhas been jailed for 12 years for
OL,8,Fattempting to rape a 13-year-old girl
OL,9,Fon a train.
OL,11,FAbdulmanon Aliev, 50, subjected a 13-
OL,12,Fyear-old girl to an "abhorrent" sexual
OL,13,Fassault on a service from Southend to
OL,14,FLondon on 16 June last year.
OL,16,FA court heard that Aliev, who was
OL,17,Fliving in Rye Lane in Peckham, south-
OL,18,Feast London, had sat opposite the
OL,19,Fvictim and attempted to use a
OL,20,Ftranslator app on his phone to speak
OL,21,Fto her.
OL,26,@tD@UOUtD@_O]
