PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1782323307
OL,3,C'Vile' predator jailed for attempting
OL,4,Cto rape 13-year-old girl on train
OL,6,FThe 13-year-old then moved away from
OL,7,Fhim to sit elsewhere, but he followed
OL,8,Fand sat next to her in an aisle seat,
OL,9,Fblocking her in by the window.
OL,11,FBritish Transport Police said Aliev
OL,12,Fthen forced himself upon the victim
OL,13,Fand subjected her to a prolonged
OL,14,Fsexual assault until the train arrived
OL,15,Fat London Fenchurch Street station
OL,16,Fwhere she was able get away from him.
OL,18,FThe victim boarded another train
OL,19,Fheading back out of London, leaving
OL,20,FAliev behind at the station.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1782323307
OL,3,C'Vile' predator jailed for attempting
OL,4,Cto rape 13-year-old girl on train
OL,6,FShe reported what happened to police
OL,7,Fand a manhunt was launched. Aliev was
OL,8,Ffound in South London and arrested him.
OL,10,FAliev was found guilty in April of
OL,11,Fattempted rape, two counts of assault
OL,12,Fby penetration and three counts of
OL,13,Fsexual assault.
OL,15,FOn Tuesday, he was sentenced to 12
OL,16,Fyears in prison with two years on
OL,17,Flicence at Inner London Crown Court,
OL,18,Fand he will be a registered sex
OL,19,Foffender for life.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
