OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1782323307
OL,3,C'Vile' predator jailed for attempting
OL,4,Cto rape 13-year-old girl on train
OL,6,FBTP Detective Constable Elizabeth
OL,7,FCahill said: "Aliev singled out a
OL,8,Fvulnerable child and subjected her to
OL,9,Fone of the most abhorrent sexual
OL,10,Fassaults I've ever investigated.
OL,12,F"While the focus of attention will
OL,13,Frightly be on him as the despicable
OL,14,Fsexual predator that he is, I want to
OL,15,Fpay tribute to the brave victim who
OL,16,Freported him to police.
OL,26,@oD@NOUtD@AOU
