PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1782323307
OL,3,C'Vile' predator jailed for attempting
OL,4,Cto rape 13-year-old girl on train
OL,6,F"His conviction and 12-year jail term
OL,7,Fwould not have been possible without
OL,8,Fher account of what happened and her
OL,9,Fwillingness to support our
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,F"We take every sexual offence report
OL,13,Fextremely seriously, and we'll stop at
OL,14,Fnothing to ensure vile offenders like
OL,15,FAliev are put behind bars where they
OL,16,Fbelong."
